<s> Omnicare Inc. , which intends to expand its position in the medical and dental markets , said it acquired a cotton and gauze products division from closely held Sterile Products Corp. for $ 8.2 million . </s>
<s> Omnicare said it expects the division to add `` substantial sales volume and to make a positive contribution to our earnings in 1990 and beyond . '' </s>
<s> In 1988 the Cincinnati company earned $ 3.1 million , or 32 cents a share , on revenue of $ 148.5 million . </s>
<s> Omnicare said the division operates under the trade name ACCO and supplies the medical and dental markets . </s>
<s> The business , based in St. Louis , had sales of more than $ 14 million in the fiscal year ended March 31 , Omnicare said . </s>
